{"tid":918690,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完新聞好想食廚師腸","createTime":"2018-11-27T12:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T16:28:45.000Z","uid":70786,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ada75ec825658a1b97fad5ead7d35477056eb6bf","tid":918690,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T12:03:34.000Z","msg":"曾經有一包未開嘅廚師腸擺喺我眼前，但係我冇去珍惜，到冇咗嘅時候先至後悔莫及，塵世間最痛苦莫過於此。如果個天可以俾個機會我返轉頭嘅話，我會買包廚師腸嚟食；如果要喺廚師腸上加個賞味期限，我希望係一萬年。"},{"pid":"1646cf09b9f614873a66a4a6aa5b3ac6160875d8","tid":918690,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"咸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8465edf21c5e7c6cbd995856770e92c35e5b19","tid":918690,"uid":5637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T15:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0573024925a901c3d69cc3380a5bfdfd011be09","tid":918690,"uid":73536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T16:28:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}